commit.message:
Drop support for Python <3.6

It's time to move on from Python 2 and, with it, Pythons below 3.6. This
is the initial work to drop the old Pythons from all our configurations.
It would be a good idea to rejigger the tox setup more comprehensively
and test on recent Pythons (up to 3.10).
